<MemberDefinition

The function is for symbol sorting when symbols have the same address.

The symbols in the same section are sorted in ascending order. llvm-objdump -D will choose the highest priority symbol to display when there are symbols with the same address.

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/mc/include/llvm/mc/mcdisassembler/mcdisassembler-h/#l00026">26</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/mc/include/llvm/mc/mcdisassembler/mcdisassembler-h">MCDisassembler.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/mc/lib/mc/mcdisassembler/mcdisassembler-cpp/#l00085">85</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/mc/lib/mc/mcdisassembler/mcdisassembler-cpp">MCDisassembler.cpp</a>.
